headline: Halliburton’s Deep Borehole Nuclear Project Adds New Angle To Valuation
summary: Halliburton (NYSE:HAL) has joined a deep borehole demonstration program for nuclear waste disposal alongside Deep Isolation and other partners. The project focuses on testing drilling and disposal technologies designed to place radioactive waste in boreholes far below the Earth's surface. The collaboration highlights a new application of Halliburton's subsurface and drilling capabilities in nuclear waste management.
